# Founder-gate / calibration outputs (may hold PRIVATE graph data — never commit to the public repo).
# cal3_fit.py / cal4_sweep.py default --out/--ckpt here; a founder run on private golds should pass an
# explicit private --out, but these guards stop an accidental leak if the default path is used.
03-evals/src/cal3_fit_results.json
03-evals/src/cal4_results.json
03-evals/src/cal3_judge.jsonl
03-evals/src/cal4_progress.jsonl

